{"tid":1893863,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【大進化】真・究極黃藍YouTube資料庫Ex 上線了","createTime":"2020-02-23T14:05:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T15:07:19.000Z","uid":107092,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"5b969f282aed8cedd0c2ca845f784e6ddad6f444","tid":1893863,"uid":107092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T14:05:04.000Z","msg":"（<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1883949/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1883949/page/1</a>）<br />\n我同咗另外一位巴打合作將兩個excel合併，<br />\n正式成為香港YouTube圖書館。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xcU9S9A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxcU9S9A.png&h=80557611&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1ncxe8ngEVQcis1_oSbidcxN0XNGUd-MTRC7D-YxrpTo/edit#gid=1926444657\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1ncxe8ngEVQcis1_oSbidcxN0XNGUd-MTRC7D-YxrpTo%2Fedit%23gid%3D1926444657&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAypriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=3ff2fd78\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1ncxe8ngEVQcis1_oSbidcxN0XNGUd-MTRC7D-YxrpTo/edit#gid=1926444657</a><br />\n圖書館嘅目的係收集以香港為本嘅YouTube Channel，<br />\n並搵出賣港賊Channel方便各位Report。<br />\n<br />\n此資料庫嘅目的純粹係為方便大家，<br />\n【並非成立大台】，<br />\n我地鼓勵各位以自己喜好把關，<br />\n選擇適合嘅頻道嚟支持。<br />\n（當然你都可以科勞曬所有同路人）<br />\n<br />\n分類嘅【目錄】係香港人Channel嘅總錄，<br />\n將會慢慢Factcheck所有頻道，<br />\n出名黃個啲就唔多講。<br />\n<br />\n【KOL100】大家都知咩事，<br />\n【賣港賊】係藍Channel總錄，<br />\n同樣都會慢慢附上Report連結。<br />\n<br />\n我地會持續收錄及補充Factcheck資訊，<br />\n謝謝各位。"},{"pid":"b2573078496fd9f3f0a4ba8b37a05dd0942eb12d","tid":1893863,"uid":107092,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T14:05:13.000Z","msg":"Q：你地同其他頻道有咩唔同？<br />\nA：此頻道不會盲目洗版叫大家入去CLSS，我地以推廣香港YouTube及捍衛本土文化為宗旨，誠心推薦及介紹不同類型嘅影片。所有影片都係我地精心挑選，<br />\n<br />\n我地相信，YouTube係捍衛香港文化嘅一道防線，係光復香港不可或缺嘅一部分。<br />\n<br />\n科勞我地：<br />\nInstagram<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/yellowyoutubehk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fyellowyoutubehk%2F&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAypriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=8079424f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/yellowyoutubehk/</a><br />\n<br />\nChannel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkyoutubelibrary/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkyoutubelibrary%2F&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAypriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=e96cf1b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkyoutubelibrary/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港YouTube總錄、影片推薦 及 各實用網站<br />\n<a href=\"https://telegra.ph/YellowYouTubeHK-02-23\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegra.ph%2FYellowYouTubeHK-02-23&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAypriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=e929d42a\" target=\"_blank\">https://telegra.ph/YellowYouTubeHK-02-23</a>"},{"pid":"37d71a76b5e1156d165fb8447c9150180dc34da9","tid":1893863,"uid":107092,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T14:05:42.000Z","msg":"想同各位講講YouTuber手足情況，<br />\n<br />\n大部分YouTuber收入有兩部分：<br />\n1 開AdSense分錢 <br />\n2 接廣告、品牌宣傳<br />\n<br />\n第一部分其實幾乎係微不足道，<br />\n大部分YouTuber一個月只有數千完，甚至更少，<br />\n加上大量不知名黃標再cut走一大段收入。<br />\n<br />\n第二部分，有公開係YouTube表態嘅手足們，<br />\n六月之後接近零廣告。<br />\n<br />\n除返開好多YouTuber手足連最低工資都冇。"},{"pid":"9ee71933ac4c7b4f0167c3a0ae76d4e5e9500dd0","tid":1893863,"uid":130568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T14:09:24.000Z","msg":"做得好好喎!加油!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0ef41d6c10c165fd779180f4bf74fb2f463223d","tid":1893863,"uid":107092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T14:10:01.000Z","msg":"香港係有好多小頻道都努力緊，<br />\n所以我地想用其他渠道打破演算法嘅限制幫佢地宣傳，<br />\n希望或多或少地幫助到佢地。<br />\n畢竟睇吃喝玩樂就成個YouTube都推薦吃喝玩樂比你，希望各位唔好淨係cls，真係欣賞下啲影片。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd31772c165241c329bd6217203762f391bca60c","tid":1893863,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T14:11:31.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: right;\">tui</div>"},{"pid":"082ff7b4d2bfb44a0d1d41c9ee0af278914135d5","tid":1893863,"uid":107092,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T14:16:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NgRgyfc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNgRgyfc.jpg&h=7ef27ca3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3846a2bc92bd295d0b7054ecf6b8798182ebd26d","tid":1893863,"uid":107092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T14:17:59.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bea6c46ee5c2c9bc933ec7462276c5cf4c51b6d7","tid":1893863,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T14:19:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />感謝手足"},{"pid":"db1740ff3336b8c80881b27630569beeec4b3f79","tid":1893863,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T14:21:13.000Z","msg":"中立撚都係自己人/同路人<br />\n唔該update返<br />\nthx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aZ1HtPR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaZ1HtPR.jpg&h=0e4d993e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"348733858dd15d00ae87caf96eecd7d70d18c53b","tid":1893863,"uid":107092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bea6c46ee5c2c9bc933ec7462276c5cf4c51b6d7","tid":1893863,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T14:19:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />感謝手足"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T14:21:17.000Z","msg":"多謝幫推"},{"pid":"68b83361539b214c5f4cb9011bfdf79beabf5b38","tid":1893863,"uid":107092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"db1740ff3336b8c80881b27630569beeec4b3f79","tid":1893863,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T14:21:13.000Z","msg":"中立撚都係自己人/同路人<br />\n唔該update返<br />\nthx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aZ1HtPR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaZ1HtPR.jpg&h=0e4d993e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T14:23:39.000Z","msg":"我都依家都冇乜改變過個諗法，<br />\n係【YouTube】上對扮黃依樣嘢。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><blockquote>點解XXX係黃？<br />\n係回答之前，<br />\n我想問下有冇藍絲質疑過何志光以前係本土派 / 社民連朋友？<br />\n有冇見過藍絲話KOL100係偽藍？<br />\n佢地冇一個出嚟派口罩嘅時候，<br />\n有冇藍絲嫌佢地做得唔夠多？<br />\n<br />\n一個Youtuber一旦公開、明顯地表態，<br />\n即使佢幾偽黃依然會被藍 / 紅嘅公司封殺，<br />\n事實上YouTube手足係六月之後就接近冇任何廣告。<br />\n當然，用光環嚟呃錢食女另計，不能接受。<br />\n<br />\n在我嘅角度，同黃色經濟圈一樣，絕對係宜鬆不宜緊。<br />\n因為各位仲可以用自己嘅個人喜好嚟把關，<br />\n你覺得佢偽黃，<br />\n嫌佢做得唔夠多之類嘅你可以唔訂閱佢、唔懲罰佢，<br />\n但佢會係榜上有名。<br />\n而且Youtuber嚟講，<br />\n做藍絲個面係絕對好做過黃好撚多，<br />\n求其拍一條鳩up片都過十萬人睇。<br />\n藍絲係唔屌鳩同路人方面係絕對值得我地學習。</blockquote></span>"},{"pid":"9edd3f828b6525a5d3caacbdf12c1243b84bf43f","tid":1893863,"uid":273703,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T14:30:28.000Z","msg":"我唔係想講黃就要比錢, 但想比大家知營運一個 YouTube channel 真係唔係免費, 你自己 break 一 break 就知營運洗費係點, 一條幾萬 view YouTube 片 Google Ads 分得千幾蚊，而黃標係直頭 0 蚊，而講 10 mins 真人片隨時要幾十個鐘 workload，時事評論可能會短好多，但背後唔洗時間準備咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Full time youtuber 呼籲人課金好合理 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔洗生活咩"},{"pid":"0c6578d3aea088e8e26a998bcc2bc0193e10b559","tid":1893863,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T14:31:03.000Z","msg":"主要係大家未知香港做二三線 Fulltime Youtuber 係幾惡劣，幾個月都冇一萬蚊收入大有人在，淨係 Comment Like Share 基本上係幫唔到 香港黃色 youtuber <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係賺大錢，係連基本生活都未必搞得掂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34c722c01555c46c05a521ee33fa4dcc7b21ad7d","tid":1893863,"uid":30201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T14:38:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a0df867fcac9e0780a8631382b85895fbc47b4a","tid":1893863,"uid":5103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T14:46:47.000Z","msg":"我地小隊依家正努力整合緊屬於我地香港本土YouTube channel<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴打們可以支持下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n攻擊重要,防守都好重要<br />\n如果出面做攻擊,我地會做好防守依一個環節<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地都仲有一班本土channel須要我地大力支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">目標對每個本土channel：subscibe+㩒鐘仔+share俾10個fd+睇片+留言+like </span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">覺唔覺得香港真係無乜本土YouTube Channel? (2.1)</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1886497\" target=\"_blank